sequenceDiagram
    actor A as Karyawan
    participant FC as FormCuti
    participant CC as CutiController
    participant DK as DataKaryawan
    participant DC as DataCuti

    A->>FC: Buka Menu Ajukan Cuti()
    A->>FC: Isi Form & Klik Submit()
    FC->>CC: Submit(Tanggal, Jenis, Alasan)
    CC->>DK: CekSisaCuti(IDKaryawan)
    DK-->>CC: Return: Sisa Kuota Cuti
    
    alt [Sisa Cuti Cukup]
        CC->>DC: SimpanCuti("Pending")
        DC-->>CC: Return: Pengajuan Disimpan
        CC-->>FC: Tampilkan Alert Sukses()
    else [Sisa Cuti Habis]
        CC-->>FC: Tampilkan Alert Gagal (Cuti Habis)()
    end
